        default boolean match(@NotNull
                      Compound y,
                      @NotNull
                      FindSubst subst)
        unification matching entry point (default implementation)
        Parameters:
        y - compound to match against (the instance executing this method is considered 'x')
        subst - the substitution context holding the match state
        Returns:
